This week has seen the start of the next eHaus showhome, as you can see in the photo the polished concrete pad will be completely wrapped in high performance insulation ensuring the warmth from the home does not leak out. The typical winter ground temperature at this site is 14 Degrees so it makes sense to completely insulate the ground from the home which will have a temperature of at least 20 degrees. If you want to follow the build as it happens step by step go to <a title="follow the build" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/EHAUS-Zero/518202518290207?fref=ts">Facebook</a>

